job_details.full_text:
AI-First Front-End Developer, Trilogy (Remote) - $60,000/year USD

* Enhance user engagement and satisfaction through the integration of advanced AI-driven features into user interfaces

profile_classification.rationale: The job description is very short and focuses on integrating AI features into user interfaces, which is a broad application. It lacks specific details about model development, data engineering, or MLOps required for ML Engineer or GenAI Engineer profiles. The emphasis on 'AI-First Front-End Developer' suggests a role that primarily uses AI tools or integrates existing AI capabilities rather than building or deeply understanding the underlying AI models. This aligns with the 'Ambiguous' profile's definition of roles primarily focused on the use of AI tools to enhance productivity or integrating AI without deep technical AI development.

job_tasks.justification: The phrase 'AI-First Front-End Developer' and 'integration of advanced AI-driven features into user interfaces' directly points to building and integrating features into user-facing applications.
This phrase describes the core activity of embedding AI capabilities into the user-facing part of an application.
job_tasks.phrase: integration of advanced AI-driven features into user interfaces
